'''刘欣如'''（{{bd|1951年||}}）是一位美国华人历史学家，印度学家。<ref name="tcnj">{{cite web |url=http://history.tcnj.edu/faculty/xinru-liu/ |title=Xinru Liu |publisher=Department of History, The College of New Jersey |access-date=2015-11-25 |archive-date=2020-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123223811/https://history.tcnj.edu/faculty/xinru-liu/ }}</ref>

==生平==
1951年出生，[[文化大革命|文化大革命]]中上山下乡耽误学业，1978年进入[[中国社会科学院|中国社会科学院]]世界史研究所担任研究员，自学英语和历史后赴美留学，1985年获得[[宾夕法尼亚大学|宾夕法尼亚大学]]博士学位。其论文发表在[[牛津大学出版社|牛津大学出版社]]名为《Ancient India and Ancient China: Trade and Religious Exchanges, A.D. 1-600》 (1988)。<ref>Book Review of Ancient India and Ancient China: Trade and Religious Exchanges, A.D. 1-600 by Jagdish P. Sharma The American Historical Review, Vol. 96, No. 1 (Feb., 1991), pp. 229-230</ref><ref>Book Review of Ancient India and Ancient China: Trade and Religious Exchanges, A.D. 1-600 in Indian Economic Social History Review 1989; 26; 121 Book Review by Shereen Ratnagar</ref>

1990年获得[[伍德罗·威尔逊国际学者中心|伍德罗·威尔逊国际学者中心]]奖学金，同时也是美国亚洲研究协会，[[美国历史学会|美国历史学会]], 世界史协会成员。<ref name="tcnj2">{{cite web|url=http://www.tcnj.edu/~liux/|title=Home Page of Xinru Liu|publisher=tcnj.edu|access-date=2015-04-05|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303230522/http://www.tcnj.edu/~liux/}}</ref><ref>Dionysus and drama in the Buddhist art of Gandhara Pia Brancaccio and Xinru Liu Journal of Global History, Volume 4, Issue 02, July 2009, pp 219-244</ref>

